# Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Text Table
# Format: XX=CHAR
# ============================================
#
# ENCODING NOTES:
# - Text is plain TBL encoded (NOT DTE compressed)
# - Text terminator: $FF (END)
# - Control codes: $F0-$FF and $22 XX (2-byte position code)
#
# Known text regions:
# - $5B400-$5B4C0: Menu text (FIGHT, ITEM, SPELL, etc.)
# - $5C2F6-$5C3C0: Casino/Poker text
# - $6E674-$6E700: Chapter titles
# - Bank 18 ($48000): Spell/Item names
#
# Generated/Updated by text analysis tools

